edspDesc: Here is the React implementation of edsp-ui, developing and serving the Sunline background products, which is an Enhanced and supplement to the antd component library.
charact1: Abstract the interactive language and visual style of the middle and back-end products from the enterprise level.
charact2: A high quality React component that is used for opening the box.
charact3: Workflow based on NPM + webpack + Babel, support ES2015.
env1: Modern browser and IE9 and above (required
label: Label
customButton: Custom buttons with a small icon style.
handleClick: The handle of the click event
nativeButtonType: Setting the type value of the button native
setButtonStyle: Setting the style of the button
title: title
isHasChangeIcon: Whether there is a handover of the content Icon
setLabelStyle: Setting the style style of the label
isHasRefresh: Do you have a refresh button
isHasClose: Do you have a close button
isHasFold: Do you have a folding button
customText: Custom character beyond the specified length display text component ellipsis, mainly on the antd component of the Tooltip expansion.
showDefaultDirect: Display the direction of the default expansion of all information
rightModalDesc: The ejection frame on the right - side excursion based on the Modal of antd.
modalWidth: The width of the pop-up frame (percentage)
tableDesc: Further encapsulation of antd's Table to enhance the Table function
lockColumn: Lock the column, not placed in the dynamic settings column
customEcharts: Custom package react echarts graphical components
